These avatars are the old default avatars featured by VRChat, these avatars consist of the winners of the "[https://medium.com/vrchat/vrchat-quest-avatar-creators-get-your-avatar-into-the-featured-row-54361c661f44 Quest Avatars]", and "[https://medium.com/vrchat/featured-avatar-row-submissions-open-68d3456b155c Featured Avatars]" jams. They can be found in the Legacy tab of the Avatars page in the [[Special:MyLanguage/Main Menu|Main Menu]].